    - usbnet/smsc75xx: silence uninitialized variable warning (Dan Carpenter)   {CVE-2023-52528}
    - tty: n_gsm: require CAP_NET_ADMIN to attach N_GSM0710 ldisc (Thadeu Lima de Souza Cascardo)  [Orabug:
    36685663]  {CVE-2023-52880}
